00:11:47.290 --> 00:11:48.820
Who were these Bazgasht poet's?

00:11:48.820 --> 00:11:51.910
Because there were poets
that actually existed in 18th

00:11:51.910 --> 00:11:55.020
and 19th Century Isfahan,
